## Project Folder Structure

The following is the main folder structure of the **YouVideo Downloader** project:

```
youvideo-downloader/
‚îÇ
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ assets/                      # Contains assets like icons, QSS themes, screenshots, etc.
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ icons/                   # Application icons (e.g., appicon.png, spinner.gif)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ qss/                     # Qt Style Sheets (dark.qss, light.qss, welcome.qss)
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ screenshot/              # Screenshots for documentation
‚îÇ
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ downloader/                  # Core download logic and ffmpeg utilities
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ __init__.py
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ ffmpeg_utils.py
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ yt_downloader.py
‚îÇ
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ ui/                          # User interface components
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ __init__.py
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ main_window.py
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ themes.py
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ welcome_screen.py
‚îÇ
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ main.py                      # Main application entry point
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ requirements.txt             # Python package dependencies
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ LICENSE                      # License file for the project
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ readme.md                    # This README file
```

